Summary: Glowing orange balls of light three of them at different times
trends: There has been one other sighting in Kincardine
There were no other sightings in Kincardine on or around May 21st 2013
divs: Sighting DetailsHappened near the harbor in Kincardine ontairo. At around 10:00 pm. Sitting on the patio at work and looked up and a orange ball of glowing light traveling across the sky. Pulled out my cell and started filming after it disappeared. A second one apered from the same as the first. It disappeared at about the same place. Then a 3rd one flew in al most same direction and disappeared a little quicker
